lifeSummary":"Thomas Brockhull是Sir William Thomas Brockhull的儿子，于大约1290年出生在英国英格兰肯特卡利爾。他和Joan Criol Lady of Brockhull至少有1个儿子。他在英国英格兰肯特薩爾特武德住了大约46年。他于1384年被列为sheriff to richard ii - thomas brockhull of calehill, in little chart, in the 6th and 7th years。他去世于1390年在英国英格兰肯特坎特布瑞享年101岁，埋葬在英国英格兰肯特坎特布瑞。"},"hr":{"Abt 1290–1390":"oko 1290.–1390.","1290–1390":"1290–1390.","1320–1383":"1320.–1383","1265–1360":"1265–1360.","May 1383":"svibanj 1383.","Abt 1377":"oko 1377.","1320":"1320.","1265":"1265","1330":"1330.","1384":"1384.","1383":"1383","1360":"1360.","Abt 1290":"oko 1290.","1390":"1390.","1290":"1290","Lewes, Sussex, England":"Lewes, Sussex, England","Hythe, Kent, England":"Hythe, Kent, England","England":"Engleska, United Kingdom","White Fryars Churchyard, Canterbury, Kent, England":"Canterbury, Kent, Engleska, United Kingdom","Brockhull, Saltwood, Kent, England":"Saltwood, Kent, Engleska, United Kingdom","Brockhill Manor, Saltwood, Kent, England":"Saltwood, Kent, England","Calehill, Kent, England":"Calehill, Kent, Engleska, United Kingdom","Canterbury, Kent, England":"Canterbury, Kent, Engleska, United Kingdom"},"cs":{"Abt 1290–1390":"okolo 1290–1390","1290–1390":"1290–1390","1320–1383":"1320–1383","1265–1360":"1265–1360","May 1383":"květen 1383","Abt 1377":"okolo 1377","1320":"1320","1265":"1265","1330":"1330","1384":"1384","1383":"1383","1360":"1360","Abt 1290":"okolo 1290","1390":"1390","1290":"1290","Lewes, Sussex, England":"Lewes, Sussex, Anglie","Hythe, Kent, England":"Hythe, Kent, Anglie","England":"Anglie, United Kingdom","White Fryars Churchyard, Canterbury, Kent, England":"Canterbury, Kent, Anglie, United Kingdom","Brockhull, Saltwood, Kent, England":"Saltwood, Kent, Anglie, United Kingdom","Brockhill Manor, Saltwood, Kent, England":"Saltwood, Kent, Anglie","Calehill, Kent, England":"Calehill, Kent, Anglie, United Kingdom","Canterbury, Kent, England":"Canterbury, Kent, Anglie, United Kingdom"},"da":{"Abt 1290–1390":"omkring 1290–1390","1290–1390":"1290–1390","1